ch.epfl.lis.wingj.structure.drosophila.wingpouch

Class WPouchStructureMeasurementsParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.epfl.lis.wingj.structure.drosophila.wingpouch.WPouchStructureMeasurementsParser

  • public class WPouchStructureMeasurementsParser
extends java.lang.Object
    Implements methods to write the measurements taken from the structure model of the wing pouch to files.

    Read method is implemented for loading benchmarks to test WingJ.

    Version:
    November 9, 2011
    Author:
    Thomas Schaffter (thomas.schaff...@gmail.com)
